figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114007c3iD0djTeUpm5GJa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802281140090eGHlATbDvQ2pPkW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114011Vsle6pHUvBjZ9Dw0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114011zmP74i5rVQTjeftM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114015pcPJBfClAXux2woT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114016qUC5vQb6ryDcN8kh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802281140170QfX987dmBIyak1g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114017oiapmJ0jHBlqNUR1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114018zJLPHv9NWMaoeqCR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114019iejmfPMrZVDvL5Wx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114021SBIi9qMQTdZ1GbWJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802281140232KkHUxQopMLO5Zzw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114023bj5s1r0KycFVR3uB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114024W4QhVojdLmE8AUrb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>不同于上一季在埃菲尔铁塔走秀，<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/fall-2018/paris/yves-saint-laurent/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Saint Laurent </a>这次把秀场放在了广阔的室内，但用成千上百个灯光背景和木地板营造出了不错的视觉效果。Saint Laurent 2018 秋冬系列的重点在于剪裁、黑色，以及闪亮的印花。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018022811405351ZO0cYKLivFTbE7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114056b7OHW59N4KAZVcTi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114056qNV8pJ5x4EkSKwtv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114057KhZFe0M5S4T9wvLc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114057ex6izv4yP9hmroLg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114058HBCgSwsnzfYNoVJy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114059qCWfyx5mDboRErje.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114059r1dmP7R6vxtZKqEV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802281141018pkoXBweWfz50nmx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802281141011wgfj0z8loiZWnKJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114101cGCFekbHE45jYiZV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802281141013aWEUhVsN4yRrPwT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114103hlxK396v1Ff5rRIt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114103AVgsLb9pexFKuO3C.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114104hDFK49rwYqAQxa2k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114105hInzfPiWDjcareOH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802281141062qAhUmBDEMjNgRKp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114107ugmMaJYiS4E67bI5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114108Mfj54A7Te0dpiL9z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114108ZT5ePQoF3jHpBvDw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114108r6f4JisNTbwHuejo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114109Mlk6tQhJcZuNp0ij.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802281141103sgmXd1AbDypUkji.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802281141113PRla7Yvuwy5CBFL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114112WzNnLHm60wOIZv5b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114113a35GmKqiyp8DwIAz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018022811411312UfHZPCbpGAJFgn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114114g7shzyG8jo9wQE1i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802281141142vYiKkLbwu3fCrBS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114115vJ1ejL4ZNk6dnVc7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114115jZO4gK3wcBCprk2t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114115QO6CMBs1p2NzW0Jr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802281141175Ei9npRNDBm2Z8vK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>赶上国际北极熊日，<a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/canada-goose-pantone-go-blue-polar-bears-1202596844/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Canada Goose </a>与色彩研究机构 Pantone 合作，推出了一款名为 PBI 的蓝色以及同名的服饰胶囊系列，以庆祝品牌支持非政府组织北极熊国际 PBI 十周年。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114141ZtuGwiQ6RJsW78Hx.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114157qXy9FDklA0Gu8shO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>伦敦牛津街的 <a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Selfridges-launches-sneaker-gallery,952180.html#.WpYgpRNuYzU\" rel=\"nofollow\">Selfridges </a>开出了一块 1776 平方英尺的运动鞋专区，以挽救女鞋卖场糟糕的业绩。 </p><p>这块区域共分为两个主题，共有 700 多种不同的球鞋。Fashion 部分引进了 Chloe、Stella McCartney、Balenciaga、Gucci 等品牌，Sneaker Head 部分包括 OFF-WHITE、Nike 等。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114212kPbg9RfGc4JjKnUi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666154\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>adidas Originals 和 Pharrell Williams 的新系列<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-02-28/hu-holi-powder-dye/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Hu Holi Powder Dye </a>来了，这一季定于 3 月 16 日正式发售，色调相当轻快。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114230yjRzPmkp1ln0vVqK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802281142357pRhGTW81kNCv3Q2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802281142329rZtTw40ijFuVdGv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.977273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114231LR3dpuJkH0vcAorx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.086364\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114231oXUCIYJes7S8Qcgk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.825758\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802281142318YxBfsMe4tIgNRaA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.586364\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114232WLA9cIJrSXupVOsd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114256Y3iR9lC8rPcdsjVW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>与法国热门餐厅 Wild &amp; the Moon 合作，OFF-WHITE 居然开始卖<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/off-white-wild-moon-blue-magic-energy/\" rel=\"nofollow\">健康功能饮料</a>了。 </p><p>这回推出的饮料共有红色和蓝色两个口味，于 2 月 24 日至 3 月 31 日期间在 Bon Marche 售卖。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802281144533HsNvG6YDcnIVw7d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114453ROiImwl6Xqdk3grt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180228114453sCqY46bRmrDvw1fh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.364729\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自 Saint Laurent</p>"}